metadata.name: Low Sleazy
metadata.description:
Low Sleazy has become a brand synonymous with community building. A culture seems to follow him as he spreads throughout the 'verse. For his consistency and permanence I wanted to create this piece on the block chain as my own graffiti to honor him.

A photoshop composite creation using a mixture of photography and MidJourney AI elements.

Created by Andrew Miller of AwesomePhotography.eth and given unconditionally without royalty or restraint. Andrew reserves the right to use the original files for portfolio and publication purposes but otherwise releases this NFT into the hands of it's owner with for commercial license in true Bored Ape fashion.
